        "created_at": "2020-08-17T00:24:45.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Arv, thanks for the report. Which is interesting, because the other cuvees I\u2019ve had from him are definitely of the darker, meatier, fuller bodied style. I\u2019ve really loved them, but they are more like a northern Rh\u00f4ne drinker\u2019s version of Beaujolais.</p>",
